ZH: 不应该把事情拖延到最后一刻。
EN: You should not procrastinate until the last minute.

ZH: 不应该随便跟陌生人分享个人信息。
EN: You should not casually share personal information with strangers.

ZH: 不应该对老师说谎。
EN: You should not lie to your teacher.

ZH: 不应该在公共场合大声喧哗。
EN: You should not make loud noises in public places.

ZH: 不应该对长辈无礼。
EN: You should not be disrespectful to elders.

ZH: 不应该忽视别人的感受。
EN: You should not ignore other people's feelings.

ZH: 不应该浪费粮食。
EN: You should not waste food.

ZH: 不应该驾驶时玩手机。
EN: You should not use your phone while driving.

ZH: 不应该随便毁坏环境。
EN: You should not randomly damage the environment.

ZH: 不应该对待动物残忍。
EN: You should not be cruel to animals.

ZH: 不应该轻易放弃。
EN: You should not give up easily.

ZH: 不应该一味听从别人意见。
EN: You should not blindly follow others' opinions.

ZH: 不应该随便迟到。
EN: You should not be casually late.

ZH: 不应该只看表面。
EN: You should not just look at the surface.

ZH: 不应该轻易放弃梦想。
EN: You should not easily give up on your dreams.

ZH: 不应该伤害他人感情。
EN: You should not hurt others' feelings.

ZH: 不应该破坏别人的信任。
EN: You should not break others' trust.

ZH: 不应该无视规则。
EN: You should not ignore the rules.

ZH: 不应该只顾自己利益。
EN: You should not only care about your own interests.

ZH: 不应该在家里大声喧哗。
EN: You should not make loud noises at home.
